FBIS4-4491 "dreas063_c_94010" FBIS-EAS-94-063 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 North Korea Radio Reports Panov Remarks on Russian Aid Radio Reports Panov Remarks on Russian Aid SK3103230094 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network in Korean 2223 GMT 31 Mar 94 SK3103230094 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network in Korean 2223 GMT 31 Mar 94 Korean BFN [Text] According to foreign reports, Russian Vice Foreign Minister Aleksandr Panov on 29 March says that Russia will render military assistance to the DPRK in accordance with the Friendship, Cooperation and Mutual Assistance Treaty signed in 1961 in the event it is invaded [chimnyak]. He stressed that the Russia Government will fulfill its treaty obligations and take steps coninciding with this purpose [mokchoke puhaptoenun chochi].
